<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 13:11:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>研究人员 3D 打印即时质谱仪的关键部件</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/researchers-3d-print-key-components-for-a-point-of-care-mass-spectrometer</link><description>2024年&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/researchers-3d-print-key-components-for-a-point-of-care-mass-spectrometer3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 13:11:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/researchers-3d-print-key-components-for-a-point-of-care-mass-spectrometer</guid></item><item><title>三名患者通过注射病毒阻止了胰腺癌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/pancreatic-cancer-halted-by-virus-injection-in-three-patients</link><description>在初步安全试验中，一种抗癌病毒已阻止三人体内的胰腺肿瘤生长和扩散，这让人们希望它可能有助于战胜这种致命疾病&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/pancreatic-cancer-halted-by-virus-injection-in-three-patients.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 12:56:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/pancreatic-cancer-halted-by-virus-injection-in-three-patients</guid></item><item><title>医源性和散发性脑淀粉样血管病患者的淀粉样蛋白 PET 负荷、脑脊液生物标志物和 APOE 基因型</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/amyloid-pet-burden-csf-biomarkers-and-apoe-genotype-in-people-with-iatrogenic-and-sporadic-cerebral-amyloid-angiopathy</link><description>该网站使用安全服务来防范恶意机器人。当网站验证您不是机器人时会显示此页面。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/amyloid-pet-burden-csf-biomarkers-and-apoe-genotype-in-people-with-iatrogenic-and-sporadic-cerebral-amyloid-angiopathy2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 12:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/amyloid-pet-burden-csf-biomarkers-and-apoe-genotype-in-people-with-iatrogenic-and-sporadic-cerebral-amyloid-angiopathy</guid></item><item><title>新型 MRI 传感器可高灵敏度检测大脑和身体中的目标分子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-mri-sensors-detect-target-molecules-in-the-brain-and-body-with-high-sensitivity</link><description>当医生和科学家想要观察身体内部时，磁共振成像 (MRI) 是一种强大的工具。 MRI 可以无创地捕获身体肌肉、器官和骨骼的详细图像。它可以监测血流以生成大脑活动图。借助麻省理工学院生物工程师开发的新传感器，核磁共振成像可以追踪使我们的大脑和身体运转的分子种类。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-mri-sensors-detect-target-molecules-in-the-brain-and-body-with-high-sensitivity2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 12:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-mri-sensors-detect-target-molecules-in-the-brain-and-body-with-high-sensitivity</guid></item><item><title>AMPK 的腺苷 2A 受体依赖性激活通过表观遗传和代谢重编程抑制 TH17 细胞致病性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/adenosine-2a-receptor-dependent-activation-of-ampk-represses-th17-cell-pathogenicity-through-epigenetic-and-metabolic-reprogramming</link><description>促进氧化代谢的表观遗传重编程可抑制 TH17 细胞的致病性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/adenosine-2a-receptor-dependent-activation-of-ampk-represses-th17-cell-pathogenicity-through-epigenetic-and-metabolic-reprogramming2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 12:11:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/adenosine-2a-receptor-dependent-activation-of-ampk-represses-th17-cell-pathogenicity-through-epigenetic-and-metabolic-reprogramming</guid></item><item><title>纳米纤维植入物提供三种药物，使胶质母细胞瘤小鼠的存活率提高一倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/nanofiber-implant-delivers-three-drugs-doubles-survival-in-glioblastoma-mice</link><description>辛辛那提大学和约翰·霍普金斯大学医学院的研究人员开发了一种治疗脑癌的潜在疗法，该疗法使用嵌入多种药物组合的纳米纤维，这些药物可以协同作用来靶向肿瘤。事实证明，这些药物联合使用比单独使用更有效，并且可以提供立即和持久的剂量来杀死癌细胞。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nanofiber-implant-delivers-three-drugs-doubles-survival-in-glioblastoma-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:56:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/nanofiber-implant-delivers-three-drugs-doubles-survival-in-glioblastoma-mice</guid></item><item><title>新技能和人工智能正在重塑工作的未来</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-skills-and-ai-are-reshaping-the-future-of-work</link><description>政策选择将决定工人和企业是否为人工智能革命做好充分准备&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-skills-and-ai-are-reshaping-the-future-of-work2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/new-skills-and-ai-are-reshaping-the-future-of-work</guid></item><item><title>试验显示，癌症疫苗可以根除患者的整个肿瘤</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cancer-jab-can-eradicate-entire-tumours-in-patients-trial-shows</link><description>在一项跨越 11 个国家的国际试验中，癌症已扩散或复发且疾病对其他治疗没有反应的患者接受了注射。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cancer-jab-can-eradicate-entire-tumours-in-patients-trial-shows.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cancer-jab-can-eradicate-entire-tumours-in-patients-trial-shows</guid></item><item><title>靶向癌症糖萼</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/targeting-the-cancer-glycocalyx</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:11:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/targeting-the-cancer-glycocalyx</guid></item><item><title>人工智能是有意识的。我们是模拟的。我们赢不了</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-is-conscious-were-simulated-and-we-cant-win</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 10:56:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026